description.content:

  • Develop a website with Elementor or Elementor Pro and ACF

Why me? :

Thanks & Regards,

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer e-commerce functionality?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I do offer via WooCommerce for the WordPress

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide support for WordPress?
What do I need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Well, Its Very Simple! I will only need three things to get started : 
1. WordPress-friendly hosting or Linux cPanel based hosting. 
2. A domain name/website name (e.g. www.google.com) linked with the hosting server. 
3. Content for pages (text, images, and videos).

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer SEO services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. I do offer On-page SEO Service. All the website will be on-page SEO-friendly. If you need more details about SEO then we can surely discuss it more by getting in touch.

questionsAndAnswers.question: As a website admin, can I manage my website myself easily?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Of course! WordPress itself provides an admin panel that can help you to manage/update/edit the website properly. I will guide you with the complete process.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I don't know how to buy Web Hosting/Domain Name?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: That's fine. I will guide you with everything. I will help you understand hosting plans, and preferred servers and will assist you until your domain and hosting plans are purchased.

Highly recommend!
